---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="Security Practices"
  descripcion="How LRA Cloud Operations handles your infrastructure security. Zero static keys, OIDC-only credentials, NDA available, GDPR compliant."
  keywords="DevOps security practices, AWS OIDC authentication, cloud infrastructure security, NDA consulting"
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #0A2540;">
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-40"
      style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(147,184,255,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 28px 28px;"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-6 py-20 sm:py-28 text-center"
    >
      <span
        class="inline-flex items-center text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6"
        style="background: rgba(30,111,255,0.2); color: #93b8ff; border: 1px solid rgba(30,111,255,0.25);"
      >
        Security
      </span>
      <h1
        class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6"
        style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
      >
        How We Handle Your Infrastructure
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto"
        style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.8);"
      >
        Security and trust practices for every engagement
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECURITY SECTIONS -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 space-y-8">
      <!-- Credential Management -->
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8"
        style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-left: 4px solid #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(10,37,64,0.04), 0 4px 16px rgba(10,37,64,0.08);"
      >
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-5">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl flex-shrink-0"
            style="background: #EEF4FF;"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5"
              style="color: #1E6FFF;"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1" style="color: #0A2540;">
              Credential Management
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm" style="color: #94a3b8;">
              Zero static keys policy
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5" style="color: #64748b;">
          We operate on a zero static keys policy. All AWS access uses OIDC
          federation with temporary credentials scoped to minimum required
          permissions. We never store, transmit or retain long-lived AWS
          credentials.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          {
            ['✓ OIDC-only', '✓ No static keys', '✓ Least privilege IAM'].map(
              (item) => (
                <span
                  class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full"
                  style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #1E6FFF; border: 1px solid #c3d9ff;"
                >
                  {item}
                </span>
              )
            )
          }
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Code & IP Ownership -->
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8"
        style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-left: 4px solid #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(10,37,64,0.04), 0 4px 16px rgba(10,37,64,0.08);"
      >
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-5">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl flex-shrink-0"
            style="background: #EEF4FF;"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5"
              style="color: #1E6FFF;"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1" style="color: #0A2540;">
              Code & IP Ownership
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm" style="color: #94a3b8;">
              Everything belongs to you from day one
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5" style="color: #64748b;">
          All code produced belongs to you from day one. We use your
          repositories, your AWS accounts, your infrastructure. At engagement
          end, we perform a complete handoff with no residual access.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          {
            [
              '✓ Your repos',
              '✓ Your accounts',
              '✓ Full handoff',
              '✓ No backdoors',
            ].map((item) => (
              <span
                class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full"
                style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #1E6FFF; border: 1px solid #c3d9ff;"
              >
                {item}
              </span>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Confidentiality -->
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8"
        style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-left: 4px solid #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(10,37,64,0.04), 0 4px 16px rgba(10,37,64,0.08);"
      >
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-5">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl flex-shrink-0"
            style="background: #EEF4FF;"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5"
              style="color: #1E6FFF;"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1" style="color: #0A2540;">
              Confidentiality
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm" style="color: #94a3b8;">
              NDA before any technical discussion
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5" style="color: #64748b;">
          We sign NDAs before technical discussions. Client details,
          architecture decisions and business context are never shared or
          referenced in public materials without explicit written consent.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          {
            [
              '✓ NDA available',
              '✓ Client anonymization',
              '✓ No public case studies without consent',
            ].map((item) => (
              <span
                class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full"
                style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #1E6FFF; border: 1px solid #c3d9ff;"
              >
                {item}
              </span>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- GDPR & Data Handling -->
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8"
        style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-left: 4px solid #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(10,37,64,0.04), 0 4px 16px rgba(10,37,64,0.08);"
      >
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-5">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl flex-shrink-0"
            style="background: #EEF4FF;"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5"
              style="color: #1E6FFF;"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1" style="color: #0A2540;">
              GDPR & Data Handling
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm" style="color: #94a3b8;">
              Cookieless analytics · No tracking
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5" style="color: #64748b;">
          Contact form data is processed via Web3Forms (GDPR compliant).
          Cloudflare Web Analytics is cookieless and anonymous. We do not use
          retargeting pixels or behavioral tracking.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          {
            [
              '✓ Cookieless analytics',
              '✓ No tracking pixels',
              '✓ Data minimization',
            ].map((item) => (
              <span
                class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full"
                style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #1E6FFF; border: 1px solid #c3d9ff;"
              >
                {item}
              </span>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 border-t border-gray-100" style="background: #F8FAFC;">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #0A2540;">
        Questions about our security practices?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base mb-8" style="color: #64748b;">
        We're happy to discuss any aspect of how we handle your infrastructure
        before starting an engagement.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white px-7 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98]"
        style="background: #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(30,111,255,0.35);"
      >
        Contact us
        <svg
          class="w-4 h-4"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
